    },
    {
        "url": "/quotes/alvin_e_roth_736175",
        "quote": "When you're doing kidney transplants, you have to find out who can exchange kidneys with whom, doing blood tests to make sure it's true. You can't just work on the preliminary data. Then you have to organize the logistics.",
