    {
        "url": "/quotes/alvin_e_roth_736173",
        "quote": "I moved to Harvard in 1998, and in 2000 the first kidney exchange in the United States was done at a hospital nearby. I started to think, 'Gee, there might be a way where I could help organize it, make it easier for people to find kidneys.'",
