    },
    {
        "url": "/quotes/alvin_e_roth_736177",
        "quote": "In a paper called 'The Economics of Matching: Stability and Incentives,' I showed that there were not any mechanisms that would always both produce a stable matching and make it completely safe for all firms and workers to reveal their true preferences.",
        "author": {
            "name": "Alvin E. Roth",
            "url": "/quotes/alvin_e_roth_736177"
